<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-justify">所需食材：</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">西葫芦1根，鸡胸肉1块，盐2克，鸡蛋2个，白胡椒粉适量，葱姜适量</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">做法：</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">1.西葫芦洗净切去根部，用擦丝器擦成丝。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200805/aaaaefbc66784fb18d663dc8e7e6bb80.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">2.鸡胸肉切成小块备用。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200805/2dd9c50ca4554dda8f0a7f82bb7e25cc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">3.将切好的鸡胸肉块和葱姜一起放入绞肉机或者料理机。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200805/035b27afc2e34c05bdf02e63a783db05.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">4.启动机器，将鸡胸肉打成鸡肉泥。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200805/3d160fa7a7d84169a10628bcc40aeb39.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">5.西葫芦丝中加入盐，打入鸡蛋，搅拌均匀。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200805/301c32fcb0b144e0bc20c8d79ef46034.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">6.将打好的鸡肉泥倒入西葫芦蛋液中，搅拌均匀。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200805/0ce89a204cad4e2dab422f51cec61641.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">7.平底锅中倒入适量的食用油，烧热，舀2勺鸡肉泥，用铲子刮平。这个不要太薄，太薄了不易定型。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200805/a950ebfa76164ca187bb778d3882af9f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">8.饼的一面凝固定型后，翻面，再煎至凝固金黄出锅。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200805/2effdeeff2c7423d8956e1fb45bfb956.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200805/fc639bd8734f4bc3bfc49036c5f8ccee.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>